globs: ["src/**/*.ts"]
alwaysApply: true
---

## ⚡ HTTP Layer
- Use **Fastify adapter** (`@nestjs/platform-fastify`) instead of Express — ~30–40% faster.
- Enable compression middleware (Brotli or Gzip).
- Implement **HTTP/2** when possible via Cloudflare.

## ✅ Database Optimization
- Use connection pooling (10–20 max connections in prod).
- Apply query caching (Redis or in-memory for frequent reads).
- Add indexes in PostgreSQL based on query patterns.
- Use TypeORM lazy relations sparingly; prefer eager loading when justified.

## ✅ API Performance
- Implement pagination & filtering in all GET endpoints.
- Use async operations efficiently; avoid blocking calls.
- Optimize JSON serialization with `@Exclude()` decorators.
- Cache short-lived responses via Redis or Cloudflare edge caching.
- Avoid N+1 queries using Supabase filters, joins, or DataLoader pattern.
